docs {
  # Test Case: Missing Required Fields
  
  This test case validates that all required fields are provided for patient registration.
  
  ## Expected Behavior
  - Should return 400 status code
  - Should return error message about missing required fields
  - Should not proceed with registration
  
  ## Test Data
  - Valid email, mobile, and OTP
  - Missing firstName and lastName (required fields)
  
  ## Required Fields for Registration
  - email (string)
  - mobileNumber (string)
  - otp (string)
  - firstName (string)
  - lastName (string)
  - dateOfBirth (string, optional)
}
